The package boost-type-index is compatible with built-in CMake targets of FindBoost.cmake:

    find_package(Boost REQUIRED COMPONENTS type_index)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::type_index)

or the generated cmake configs via:

    find_package(boost_type_index REQUIRED CONFIG)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::type_index)
